{"tid":1608474,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【鍵盤戰線】一齊係10月1推呢個hashtag上twitter熱門","createTime":"2019-10-01T10:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T10:28:01.000Z","uid":243871,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dacd2d4360955c2991be0c6959b95c2ce7d54b00","tid":1608474,"uid":243871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"各位 今日係10月1 當然要賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依加咁多手足係外面為我哋搏命<br />\n（希望各位平平安安返到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n出唔到去嘅手足 其實都有好多嘢可以做到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如：刷Twitter同埋其他社交媒體<br />\n<br />\n我哋要比外國知 10月1對香港嚟講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係國殤日 唔係國慶日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我之前見有媒體用 &quot;National day of mourning&quot;<br />\n覺得唔錯 所以就用佢嚟發tweet<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzbGDAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzbGDAi.jpg&h=58189012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家意下如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家都可以幫手諗吓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之 一定要賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb03bd5ecc340c69d330255accdf82d90338667","tid":1608474,"uid":243871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"#nationaldayofmourning<br />\n#沒有國慶只有國殤"},{"pid":"4449091134c1dddd879b18a0f7ec42cc34ad8f2f","tid":1608474,"uid":243871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:20:42.000Z","msg":"推埋手足中彈片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cityusuedb/status/1178966032733487105?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcityusuedb%2Fstatus%2F1178966032733487105%3Fs%3D21&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=b80ab8c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%